<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90"><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/powerapps/maker/portals/admin/upgrade-portal" sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90">Upgrade a portal</a></li>
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="91"><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/powerapps/maker/portals/admin/migrate-portal-configuration" sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="91">Migrate portal configuration</a></li>
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57777" sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-setup.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">Solution Lifecycle Management: Dynamics 365 for Customer Engagement apps</a></li>
</ul>
